#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/resteasy-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you want to stream JSON objects in your response, you can use\n"
"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/server-sent-events.html[Server-Sent Events]\n"
